## 1️⃣ Allowed Use (Permitted)

- **Personal use:** Planning your trip, family/parenting guidance, and on-the-ground navigation.
- **Educational use:** Learning how to navigate China, training materials, and classroom discussion.
- **Sharing:** Copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format for non-commercial purposes.
- **Attribution:** You must give appropriate credit to **"MilesXLab / ChinaOps"**.

## 2️⃣ Prohibited Use (Commercial Restrictions)

**Commercial use is strictly prohibited without explicit written permission.** You may NOT:

- **Sell or charge** for access to ChinaOps content (Markdown files, PDFs, website, or derived tools).
- **Incorporate** content into a paid subscription, paid course, commercial travel guide, or paid app.
- **Remove or alter** the original attribution, credits, or "Terms of Use" notices.
- **Republish** as your own work for any commercial purpose (direct or indirect monetisation).

Any commercial exploitation of ChinaOps content constitutes a license violation and will be pursued.

## 3️⃣ Official Access & Integrity

Always access the most accurate and up-to-date version of ChinaOps via the official channels:
- **GitHub Repository:** [https://github.com/MilesXLab/ChinaOps](https://github.com/MilesXLab/ChinaOps)
- **Official Portal:** [https://milesxlab.github.io/ChinaOps/](https://milesxlab.github.io/ChinaOps/)

Tools and interactive features (PDF export, maps, calculators) are tied to official services. Cloned copies or third-party mirrors may not function correctly and are not supported.

## 4️⃣ Contribution & Community

- **Contributions:** Pull Requests are welcome to improve content (additional cities, SOP updates, corrections).
- **Feedback:** Report commercial clones, outdated info, or license violations via [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/MilesXLab/ChinaOps/issues).
- **Discussions:** General suggestions and feedback can be shared on GitHub Discussions.

